Package com.archql.labs.householddevices

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    IDeviceFilter
    device filter
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Device
    class that holds general information of an abstract device property name refers to a product name property price refers to its cost property manufacturerName refers to a company name that produced the item property article refers to a unique code assigned to the item by manufacturer property isOnStall reflects if object is currently can be bought property price refers to its type
    Fridge
    class fridge that holds general information of a fridge device property power refers to a power consumption in watts property height refers to its height in cm property width refers to its width in cm property color refers to color
    Kettle
    class Kettle that holds general information of a Kettle device property power refers to a power consumption in watts property material refers to its material property hasWhistle whether kettle has a whistle installed property color refers to color
    RobotVacuum
    class RobotVacuum that holds general information of a RobotVacuum device property timeToWork refers to time in h which robot can work autonomously property areaToWork refers to area that it can cover in m^2 property color refers to color
  • Enum Summary
